      "text": "And from that railroad station, they marched us, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] hundreds of people, marched us to a destination which we didn't know, of course, what it was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And eventually, we arrived to an area which was fenced with barbed wires and gates and barbed wires and towers, guard towers.",
